#   `Keys::new(secret_key)` / `keys.public_key()` /
#   `keys.secret_key()` keypair primitives, the typed
#   `EventBuilder::text_note(content)
#   .tags(tags).sign_with_keys(keys)` /
#   `EventBuilder::metadata(meta).sign_with_keys(keys)` /
#   `EventBuilder::contact_list(contacts).sign_with_keys(keys)`
#   /  `EventBuilder::repost(repost_event)
#   .sign_with_keys(keys)` / `EventBuilder::reaction(event,
#   reaction).sign_with_keys(keys)` event builders, the
#   typed `Filter::new().authors(vec![pk]).kinds(vec![
#   Kind::TextNote]).limit(20).since(timestamp).until(
#   timestamp).search("query").hashtag("nostr").event(eid)
#   .reference("e").identifier("d")` filter builder, every
#   typed `Kind::Metadata` / `TextNote` / `RecommendRelay`
